'''高氯酸镥'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为Lu(ClO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。它可以形成水合物Lu(ClO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>·n H<sub>2</sub>O（n=3、6<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Zeitschrift für anorganische und allgemeine Chemie|volume=625|issue=9|language=de|issn=0044-2313|date=1999-09|pages=1556–1561|doi=10.1002/(SICI)1521-3749(199909)625:93.0.CO;2-K|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/(SICI)1521-3749(199909)625:93.0.CO;2-K|title=Perchlorato Complexes of Rare-Earth Elements: Syntheses and Crystal Structures of Lu(ClO4)3 · 3 H2O, Er(ClO4)3 · H2O, and Sc(OH)(ClO4)2 · H2O|accessdate=2020-08-19|author=Mathias S. Wickleder}}</ref>或8<ref name=Belkova />）和[[二甲基亚砜|DMSO]]合物Lu(ClO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>·7DMSO<ref>Lugina, L. N.; Davidenko, N. K. Complexes of lanthanides with dimethyl sulfoxide in nitromethane. ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1980. 25 (9): 2393-2399. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>。

它的水合物可由[[氧化镥|氧化镥]]和[[高氯酸|高氯酸]]反应，结晶得到，真空下经[[六氧化二氯|Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>6</sub>]]脱水得到无水物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=139|issue=2|language=en|date=1998-09|pages=259–265|doi=10.1006/jssc.1998.7838|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459698978380|title=Crystalline and Molecular Structures of Anhydrous Lanthanide PerchloratesLn(ClO4)3withLn=La, Ce, Pr, Sm, Eu, Ho, Er, Tm, and Lu|accessdate=2020-08-19|author=J.L. Pascal, F. Favier, F. Cunin, A. Fitch, G. Vaughan|archive-date=2018-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180605183448/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022459698978380|dead-url=no}}</ref>

